    <briefdescription>
<para>Base class for all hardware-polled input objects on a <ref refid="namespacePanelGroup" kindref="compound">PanelGroup</ref> board. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Subclass this to create custom input handlers. Objects self-register at construction; <ref refid="namespacePanelGroup_1ab31c183f1fe58194e9c6e512fd9a0371" kindref="member">PanelGroup::loop()</ref> calls <ref refid="classOpenSkyhawk_1_1InputBase_1abe4599c9fd224766d742761261391b45" kindref="member">poll()</ref> on every object each iteration. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
